data.description: Discover your peaceful oasis on this private 10-acre estate! The spacious brick home features 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and a bonus room. Natural light fills the living room, offering scenic views of the front yard and majestic oak trees. The kitchen with ample counterspace and dual dining areas is ideal for entertaining. The garage conversion offers an expansive bonus living area and an additional bonus room serves as an office or 4th bedroom. The bedrooms are generously sized, and the master suite includes two closets and an ensuite. This exceptional property has everything for horse lovers, including 2 roping arenas (one currently used as a horse pen), a horse barn, and a storage shed. Mature shade trees and a pond in the back add to the tranquil ambiance. Seize the opportunity to embrace country life with easy access to Beeville, Sinton, and Calallen. This is a great location for your horse or hobby farm. Don't miss your chance to turn your country living dreams into a reality!
